      "blocks": {
        "question-1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What Terrains Can I Ride My Tyson In?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>The ability to ride in all-terrain is one of the benefits of fat-tire electric bikes, like the Tyson. There are virtually no roads that are off-limits with Tyson! Its 4-inch fat tires combine with 750Wh motor give riders outstanding traction on even the most troublesome terrain.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What Is The Superiority Of One-Piece Body?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>The biggest advantage of one-piece injection molding technology is that the products are molded quickly, and the overall stability, as well as shaping the shape of the effect are better, so that the use of the product will be safer, the quality will be better, more in line with the scientific, safe use of the requirements and standards.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What Are the Advantages of One-Piece Wheel?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Pressure cushioning and shock resistance are better than spoked, while not easy to fatigue. Handlebars can be freely extended even on steep hills, so it is more suitable for mountain biking and cross-country travel.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Is Tyson's LCD Display The Latest Version?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Standard with TFT-LCD Display, clearer and supports 4G as well.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
